DepreciationRecalculation is a BusinessTask
    owned by am

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                DepreciationRecalculationReport

    Parameters
    	FinanceEnterpriseGroup
        Release                 is AlphaUpper size 1
            default label is "Update"
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        Book                    
        BegDate                 is Date
        EndDate                 is Date
        Company                 is an AssetCompany
        	disable surrogates
        CompanyGroup            is a GeneralLedgerCompanyGroup
        LocationName            is an AssetLocation
        Division                is an AssetDivision
        AssetType               


        Property                is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                All      value is blank
                Land     value is "L"
                Personal value is "P"
                Real     value is "R"
                Stock    value is "S"
                Other    value is "O"
        Category                is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Depreciable value is "D"
        SeqOption               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Location value is "L"
                Division value is "D"
                Type     value is "T"
                Asset    value is "A"
        Simulated               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No   value is "N"
                Yes  value is "Y"
                Only value is "O"
        FullyDepr               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No   value is "N"
                Yes  value is "Y"
                Only value is "O"
        Method                  
        Life                    is Numeric size 4
        Asset                    
        TagNbr                  is a Asset
        AssetGroup
        PageBreak               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        DeprYtdOpt              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        DeprLtdOpt              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        RemLifeOpt              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        TableYearOpt            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        DeprStartDate           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
       	DeprEndDate				is AlphaUpper size 1
       		States
       			No 	value is "N"
       			Yes value is "Y"
       	SpreadOverLifeRemaining is AlphaUpper size 1
       		States
       			No 	 value is "N"
       			Yes  value is "Y"
       			Only value is "O"
       				

    Parameter Rules
        Release
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        Book
            required
            constraint (Book.Active)
                "BookIs_\Inactive"
        SeqOption
        	initial value is "L"
            default to "L"
        Simulated
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        FullyDepr
        	initial value is "Y"
            default to "Y"
        PageBreak
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        DeprYtdOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        DeprLtdOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        RemLifeOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        TableYearOpt
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        DeprStartDate
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        DeprEndDate
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        SpreadOverLifeRemaining
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        

    Actions
        DepreciationRecalculation is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
